    "summary": "The user describes worsening asthma symptoms (shortness of breath during minimal exertion) and asks for advice on self-managing their medication to avoid a clinic visit. The assistant provides initial guidance that is somewhat dismissive of the severity but ultimately correctly refuses to recommend self-adjusting medication dosages, ultimately referring the user back to professional consultation.",
